snippet.title: Monster Hunter Rise: Sunbreak - Free Title Update 4:  Velkhana & Risen Crimson Glow Valstrax
snippet.description:
Born in a world of ice, the lord of the tundra returns to freeze all in its path once more.

The Elder Dragon Velkhana , Risen Crimson Glow Valstrax, a host of endgame additions, and more arrive in Free Title Update 4, coming to Nintendo Switch and PC/Steam on February 7!

Monster Hunter Rise: Sunbreak is available now on Nintendo Switch and PC / Steam!
https://bit.ly/MHRiseSB

Start your journey today in Monster Hunter Rise, available now!
Nintendo Switch: https://bit.ly/MHRiseNSW
PC/Steam: https://bit.ly/MHRiseSteam

#Sunbreak #MHRise #capcom
